          "_name": "features10",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features10\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitleCard\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#fafafa\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background5.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Our Commitment to Excellence</b></h3>\n            <h4 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                Subtitle\n            </h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Mission</b></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                                $39</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\"><b>Mission:<br></b><br>To empower aspiring professionals with industry-ready, job-oriented skills through hands-on learning, real-world labs, and practical mentorship.<br><br>Our mission is to bridge the gap between academic knowledge and real-world expertise by delivering training that reflects actual industry environments — not just theory.<br><br>We focus on:<br><br>✔ Practical implementation over memorization<br>✔ Real-world DevOps, Cloud, and Automation scenarios<br>✔ Resume-building through hands-on projects<br>✔ Confidence building through guided mentorship<br><br>Our goal is simple:<br>✔ Make you employable, confident, and technically strong.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Vision</b></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                                $39</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\"><b>Vision:<br></b><br>To become a leading platform for industry-focused online technical education, recognized for producing skilled professionals who are ready to contribute from Day One in real-world environments.<br><br>We envision:<br><br>✔ A community of highly skilled DevOps &amp; Cloud engineers<br>✔ Learning that evolves with industry trends<br>✔ Training that prioritizes job readiness over certifications<br>✔ Professionals who solve problems, not just clear exams<br>✔ We aim to create a generation of engineers who understand how things actually work in production.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Our core values</b></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                                $39</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\"><b>Core Values:<br></b><br>✔ Practical First Approach<br>We believe real learning happens when you build, break, debug, and deploy — not just watch videos.<br><br>✔ Industry Relevance<br>Our curriculum reflects current industry demands including DevOps, Cloud, Automation, Containers, CI/CD, and modern infrastructure.<br><br>✔ Transparency<br>No fluff. No unrealistic promises. Clear roadmap. Clear expectations.<br><br>✔ Mentorship &amp; Support<br>Learning is easier when guided. We focus on interaction, doubt-solving, and real-time problem discussions.<br><br>✔ Continuous Growth<br>Technology evolves — and so do we. Our courses are updated to reflect modern tools and best practices.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
